<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of the sons of Korah; set to Alamoth. A song.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />God is our refuge and strength,</para>

<para style="q1">a very present help in trouble.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Therefore we will not fear, though the earth should change,</para>

<para style="q1">though the mountains should be shaken into the heart of the seas,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />though its waters roar and rage, and</para>

<para style="q1">though the mountains tremble with their swelling.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>

<para style="b" />
